Package maps

Interface Summary
CoordinateConversion Interface for converting coordinates from one system to another.
Map Top-level interface for all types of map.
MapFormat Interface for different types of map format.
 

Class Summary
ConstantConversion A coordinate conversion that multiplies by a number.
IdentityConversion A no-op coordinate conversion.
MapReader A utility class for reading maps.
MapTools Utility class for dealing with maps.
MapWriter A class for writing maps.
ScaleConversion A coordinate conversion that scales and translates coordinates.
 

Exception Summary
MapException Exceptions related to maps.
